description:
An app that knows which song is to be found in which book at which page. 
With this app you can find out on what page a song is to be found in a songbook.
The dataset contains mostly books with scouting context.
You can search by keywords, categorys or browse the books list of contents.
It also provides a button to randomly choose a song.

The dataset which can be updated in-app stands under the CC BY-SA DE License.
